        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139290_000005_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139290/1425_139290_000005_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "They seldom come nearer to it than planting time, harvest time, cherry time, spring time, or fall time.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139290_000005_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139290/1425_139290_000005_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "I was not allowed to make any inquiries of my master concerning it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139290_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139290/1425_139290_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "She was the daughter of Isaac and Betsey Bailey, both colored, and quite dark.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139290_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139290/1425_139290_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "He was admitted to be such by all I ever heard speak of my parentage.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139290_000007_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139290/1425_139290_000007_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "The opinion was also whispered that my master was my father; but of the correctness of this opinion, I know nothing; the means of knowing was withheld from me.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139290_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139290/1425_139290_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "She was hired by a mr Stewart, who lived about twelve miles from my home.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139290_000008_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139290/1425_139290_000008_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "She was with me in the night.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139290_000008_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139290/1425_139290_000008_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "I was not allowed to be present during her illness, at her death, or burial.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139290_000008_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139290/1425_139290_000008_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "She was gone long before I knew any thing about it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139290_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139290/1425_139290_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "I have had two masters.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139290_000012_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139290/1425_139290_000012_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "He was generally called Captain Anthony-a title which, I presume, he acquired by sailing a craft on the Chesapeake Bay. He was not considered a rich slaveholder.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139290_000012_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139290/1425_139290_000012_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "It required extraordinary barbarity on the part of an overseer to affect him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139290_000012_000012",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139290/1425_139290_000012_000012.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "He would at times seem to take great pleasure in whipping a slave.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139290_000012_000013",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139290/1425_139290_000012_000013.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "I have often been awakened at the dawn of day by the most heart rending shrieks of an own aunt of mine, whom he used to tie up to a joist, and whip upon her naked back till she was literally covered with blood.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139290_000012_000017",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139290/1425_139290_000012_000017.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "I was quite a child, but I well remember it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139290_000012_000020",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139290/1425_139290_000012_000020.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "It struck me with awful force.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139290_000012_000022",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139290/1425_139290_000012_000022.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "It was a most terrible spectacle.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139290_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139290/1425_139290_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "This occurrence took place very soon after I went to live with my old master, and under the following circumstances.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139290_000013_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139290/1425_139290_000013_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "Aunt Hester went out one night,--where or for what I do not know,--and happened to be absent when my master desired her presence.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139290_000013_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139290/1425_139290_000013_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "Why master was so careful of her, may be safely left to conjecture.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139290_000014_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139290/1425_139290_000014_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "She now stood fair for his infernal purpose.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139290_000014_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139290/1425_139290_000014_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "Her arms were stretched up at their full length, so that she stood upon the ends of her toes.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139290_000014_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139290/1425_139290_000014_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "I was so terrified and horror stricken at the sight, that I hid myself in a closet, and dared not venture out till long after the bloody transaction was over.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139290_000014_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139290/1425_139290_000014_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "I expected it would be my turn next.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139290_000014_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139290/1425_139290_000014_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "It was all new to me. I had never seen any thing like it before.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139291_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139291/1425_139291_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "My master's family consisted of two sons, Andrew and Richard; one daughter, Lucretia, and her husband, Captain Thomas Auld.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139291_000001_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139291/1425_139291_000001_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "The principal products raised upon it were tobacco, corn, and wheat.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139291_000001_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139291/1425_139291_000001_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "Their names were peter, Isaac, Rich, and Jake.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139291_000005_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139291/1425_139291_000005_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "His career was short.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139291_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139291/1425_139291_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "He was a very different man.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139291_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139291/1425_139291_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "All the mechanical operations for all the farms were performed here.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139291_000007_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139291/1425_139291_000007_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "He was called the smartest and most trusty fellow, who had this honor conferred upon him the most frequently.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139291_000008_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139291/1425_139291_000008_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "Especially would they do this, when leaving home.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139297_000000_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139297/1425_139297_000000_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "CHAPTER eight",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139297_000001_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139297/1425_139297_000001_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "He died while on a visit to see his daughter at Hillsborough.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139297_000001_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139297/1425_139297_000001_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "Cut off thus unexpectedly, he left no will as to the disposal of his property.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139297_000001_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139297/1425_139297_000001_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "I was immediately sent for, to be valued with the other property.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1425_139297_000001_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1425/139297/1425_139297_000001_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1425",
        "content": "I took passage with Captain Rowe, in the schooner Wild Cat, and, after a sail of about twenty four hours, I found myself near the place of my birth.",
